			</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>DIA_MOREDG_DREPA_DESCRIPTION</LocID>
				<Text>鎌状赤血球症は、鎌状赤血球貧血とも呼ばれ、赤血球中のヘモグロビンに影響を及ぼす遺伝性の疾患です。</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>DIA_MOREDG_WILLEBRAND</LocID>
